    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This beauty is in truly flawless shape\u2014inside and out, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken obsessive care of it, so you won\u2019t find a single scratch or dent anywhere. It drives like a cloud and still has that fresh, new-car feel. I\u2019m looking for a smooth, easy sale to someone who will love it as much as I have. You\u2019ve got to see this one in person to believe it\u2014come take a look and let's get you behind the wheel! \u2728",
