      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_26_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_26",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s engineering peak, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock, providing exceptional torque transfer. Critically, the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings have been serviced to ensure long-term mechanical synchronization. The suspension retains its original geometry with zero bushing deflection, offering the precise turn-in and lateral stability expected of a concours-level specimen. Every body panel retains its factory-correct mill thickness, and the interior is free of the typical soft-touch delamination, making this a turn-key investment for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
